            Best for: Gear, apps, travel services
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Option 2 -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-concrete/20 bg-bedrock flex flex-col">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-orange mb-2">Ad-Break Sponsorship</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-concrete mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">Dedicated Segment</p>
          <p class="text-off-white/90 mb-6 flex-grow">
            A dedicated 30-60 second focused segment within the video. High production value, custom script, and clear call-to-action.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-concrete space-y-2 mb-8">
